fields.name: Pancakes
fields.description: Indulge in the delightful and timeless comfort of homemade pancakes with our irresistible recipe. These golden-brown discs of fluffy goodness are a classic breakfast staple that never fails to bring joy to the table. With their tender texture and enticing aroma, our pancakes are the perfect canvas for your favorite toppings, whether it's a drizzle of maple syrup, a dollop of creamy butter, a sprinkle of fresh berries, or a handful of crunchy nuts. Whether you're enjoying a lazy weekend morning or a quick weekday treat, these pancakes are sure to brighten your day with their warm and inviting taste.
fields.ingredients:
1 cup all-purpose flour
2 tablespoons granulated sugar
1 teaspoon baking powder
1/2 teaspoon baking soda
1/4 teaspoon salt
3/4 cup buttermilk
1/4 cup milk
1 large egg
2 tablespoons unsalted butter, melted
1 teaspoon vanilla extract
Cooking spray or additional butter for greasing the pan
